						               													<description>For party and holiday!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Combined bid, luck, contest in a game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The rules are simple, the process of stimulation, and yet joyous explosion point game depth, especially for playing together in the New Year with their families!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is not only a game, but also is table decorations!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Do follow 7 steps in a round:&amp;#10;Step 1: Auction to become the banker.&amp;#10;Step 2: The banker pay into Money Pool, choose a Race Card and receive 6 Point Cards.&amp;#10;Step 3: All player except banker place a Large/Small Betting Card.&amp;#10;Step 4: All player except banker guess the banker's Point Cards.&amp;#10;Step 5: Show Point Cards and distribute the Money Pool to those players who made the correct bet.&amp;#10;Step 6: The banker moves statues of deities forward.&amp;#10;Step 7: End the current round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Race Card is worth $80 for the first place, 60 for the second place, 30 for the third place, 0 for the fourth place. Each player sum the values of Game Coins and Race Cards in his/her possession. The player with the largest sum wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
